data.description: Located in the Lake Jackson farms subdivision, this beautiful home offers an open/ split floor plans with high ceilings throughout. There are 4 bedrooms, 3 full and 2 half baths, formal dining room, office with French doors, large indoor utility room and a 3 car attached garage. The kitchen has an island with gas cooktop, breakfast bar, pantry and lots of counter top space & cabinets for storage. The oversized downstairs primary suite has room for a sitting area and the en suite has double sinks with vanity, soaking tub with separate shower, powder room and large walk in closet. The other 3 bedrooms are upstairs along with a flex space that could be used for a game room, gym space, etc. Big backyard with a nice size patio to sit and enjoy a cup of coffee. Conveniently located close to schools, shopping, dining, Hwy 288, etc. This is the one you have been waiting for! Don't miss the chance to make it yours, call us to see today!
